-You're lying.

585
01:04:15,116 --> 01:04:16,980
Bitch.

586
01:04:17,017 --> 01:04:18,507
Whore.

587
01:04:20,888 --> 01:04:23,588
Cunt!

588
01:04:24,725 --> 01:04:26,955
