658
01:10:28,462 --> 01:10:30,054
You don't know him.

659
01:10:39,240 --> 01:10:41,002
Be lucky.

660
01:10:42,308 --> 01:10:44,003
Come on, guys.

661
01:10:51,351 --> 01:10:53,519
Ready?

662
01:10:53,520 --> 01:10:56,683
Peter,the first few minutes...

663
01:10:56,723 --> 01:10:58,452
