-Yeah, I think she is.

727
01:22:13,187 --> 01:22:15,710
Can you get me
out of this fucking suit?

728
01:22:37,709 --> 01:22:38,875
Yeah, Cole here.

729
01:22:38,876 --> 01:22:40,969
-Cole, it's Novak.
-Yeah, what's up?

730
01:22:41,012 --> 01:22:43,105
